node.text: @aliciacho ikr! thanks to sg! We get to find lotsa cuisine even when we cant travel 😊

Cant go Taiwan so get our food craving fixed from @emosnackssg!

Ordered their braised pork rice to try and we are super satisfied with it. It's very filling! Braised pork is tender and look at those fats 🤤 偶尔吃不会罪过啦! Salted veg taste just right too! Not forgetting their crispy enoki, honey milk tea, thai milk tea are all good.

Check them out to support small biz during this period of time okay! PS. This is not a sponsored post 😊
